What this click service is, is it's trying to solve a problem of getting or latency issues between like, Asia versus the rest of the world, etcetera. So, for example, whenever turbine is propagating the blocks or the shreds over to the different validators across the world, some validators might get them late sometimes because of location across the world. So this click service, what it does is it kind of creates clicks or it's optional clicks, so where a validator can forward directly parallel to the normal retransmit stage to the validators that they choose.
